comments.body:
@nick-lehmann Below is a pointer to current API documentation.  It's a work in progress, please let us know what you find confusing or missing :-)  We are using swagger annotations on the go code to create this documentation. 

The main driver here is we're moving to a REST-like API, the endpoints that include /libpod/ have all the goodies from Podman included.  An example, would be pods.  

https://podman.readthedocs.io/en/latest/Reference.html
